public class CMDFunction<P,R,I,M>
extends FunctionMetaDataFunction<P,R,CompositeMetaData<I,M>>

This class provides a CMDFunction (= CompositeMetaDataFunction). It is an implementation of MetaDataFunction that uses a hash map to store the meta data.
